      "truth": "inference",
      "checkClass": "C0",
      "depth": "L5",
      "from": "SEED (root intent)",
      "ada:whyItMatters": "The map the surface is built inside. Without it, the TUI is restyled from taste-of-the-day instead of a governed model.",
      "ada:failureIfMissing": "Each screen gets designed in isolation; the shell drifts into confetti and inconsistency.",
